snippet.title: Vibrant Venture Steam Gameplay Trailer #1
snippet.description:
The Steam store page is now open! You can find and wishlist the game here: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1264520/

Vibrant Venture is an upcoming 2D platformer adventure game with puzzle elements. The game features four characters with unique abilities that can be combined to traverse the world!

Follow Pattrigue on Twitter for game updates:
https://twitter.com/Pattrigue

Join our Discord and talk to us:
https://discord.gg/SSUTPCU
